{"tid":1053070,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"大家點睇賓得呢個牌子？","createTime":"2019-03-08T17:53:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-10T06:31:16.000Z","uid":191921,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2269edf9e58eae56954237800b0ac46b820134da","tid":1053070,"uid":191921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T17:53:40.000Z","msg":"今年的 11 月 27 日更是 Pentax 創立 100 周年的大日子。Ricoh 日前宣布，從 2019 年到 2020 年，將在日本及國外推出一系列的紀念及慶祝活動"},{"pid":"5a767db45b7af487de02388dcfec55d01a6d9397","tid":1053070,"uid":191921,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T18:01:18.000Z","msg":"特別幸運，Pentax擁有其他品牌所沒有的神兵利器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />GPS-1，一個可讓你對準天空拍攝最多5分鐘，不讓星星因著地球自轉而變星軌的功能。這一兩年Pentax更將OGPS-1內建在K-3II、K-1這兩個機種，稱之為astrotracer，這讓Pentax的星空攝影玩家進一步把其他品牌遠遠拋在千里之外。"},{"pid":"c56d29a5f907680ecde096a49a39463a5c7d9f43","tid":1053070,"uid":71341,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T23:20:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f38c56c75150273ec87e23a91713bf9612bf6b49","tid":1053070,"uid":117044,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T23:26:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"01dcd67e2b802743decd205f4471a8cae78a3b32","tid":1053070,"uid":5542,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T00:36:45.000Z","msg":"機身硬 鏡頭出色 代理廢<br />\n<br />\n第一部機就係k100d super"},{"pid":"cea30a388ac4faed972f3fb2e002754d13ec6efe","tid":1053070,"uid":191921,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f38c56c75150273ec87e23a91713bf9612bf6b49","tid":1053070,"uid":117044,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"c56d29a5f907680ecde096a49a39463a5c7d9f43","tid":1053070,"uid":71341,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T23:20:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T23:26:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T00:54:56.000Z","msg":"認真post, 勿膠化"},{"pid":"054befad4f34547869a3f3b3b3d582df2c6e7853","tid":1053070,"uid":191921,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T01:14:49.000Z","msg":"個人尼講係好欣賞呢個品牌，其實用左全力用心去整相機除左上述astrotracer黑科技, 佢有幾點係非常屈機<br />\n<br />\n1. 單反五軸防震，雖然以前minolta 都有，仲做到五級，只此一家<br />\n<br />\n2. 單反chok 像素，36mp手持都得，只此一家<br />\n<br />\n3. 單反多角度扭mon, 唔係只得x y 軸旋轉，而係全方位任扭<br />\n4. 戰地級應用機身，最堅固body 同鏡頭應該無人會質疑，入左沙再沖水都完全無事。。。<br />\n<br />\n5. 真正靚色水，唔係泥坑專影景或奸狼影人個隻偏色，更唔係味精富士個隻明顯斧鑿過的，或者真實都到有時唔好睇的sony，唔敢講賓得色最靚，但搵到個平衡點，幾乎係無可挑剔<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">簡單講句，如果純影靜態又想直出，K1 好可能係最佳選擇。<br />\n<br />\n但問題係部機對焦明顯落後其他機，副廠同二手鏡頭太少，配件玩燈各樣都係難搵，配粒二手電都麻煩過人，所以入得場都好難走。講咁多都係想多d 人識欣賞同支持唔同機種，任何牌子收皮都係玩家損失。</span></span>"},{"pid":"3fa19573b04bfcb35d23e53b9862e3249131af2d","tid":1053070,"uid":191921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01dcd67e2b802743decd205f4471a8cae78a3b32","tid":1053070,"uid":5542,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T00:36:45.000Z","msg":"機身硬 鏡頭出色 代理廢<br />\n<br />\n第一部機就係k100d super"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T01:17:16.000Z","msg":"其實唔明點解個對焦咁多年都咁屎，nikon 同一塊對焦module 都用左十幾年，到而家都好好用，pentax 改善到對焦真係完美單反"},{"pid":"3fdb3e23363dcd5c199710068c121f2a1b4869cb","tid":1053070,"uid":70977,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T05:22:58.000Z","msg":"一路都對三公主好有幻想 有冇人玩過分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb2e2a8ca29814b058495ccba3255f5b3d17e524","tid":1053070,"uid":143349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T06:46:27.000Z","msg":"戰地記者專用品牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n朋友有部K1 之前試玩過<br />\n手感好紮實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84c0998074c5c5e38635aa3854ff87d9d0319c42","tid":1053070,"uid":144871,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-1